description:
As a user of Shopline
  I want to create order with member tier products
  So that order can be created sucessfully (price should display member tier price)
name: manually create member price tier product order - logged in

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field

I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button

I click on add button

I fill "(dirty data) member tier level 1" to membership tier name field

I fill "20" to member offer field
I click on submit button

I am on Membership Tier Setting Page
I click on add button
I should be redirected to Membership Tier New Page

I click on submit button
I should be redirected to Membership Tier Setting Page
I should see row of membership list
I am on Product Create Page
I pick product photo to product photo selector
I should see delete photo button
I click on info tab
I fill "(dirty data) 1 layer product for member tier price" to english name field
